Lasius
=================================

Lasius is a simple online time booking and tracking platform inspired by hamster and aims to provided 
an easy interface to book your daily work time on different projects/tasks.

The second goal of Lasius is to combine several different kind of techniques/architecture, all of 
used in their main scope:
- DDD/CQRS for Time Booking operations
- TypedId -> Use typed id as primary and foreign keys, use implicit convertion wherever possible
